text.section:
The following licensees are exempt from any issuing fee on any class of license:
Persons holding alcoholic beverages licenses prior to July 1, 1987;
A corporation holding an alcoholic beverages license that has a 50 percent or less change of its corporate officers;
A nonprofit corporation, fraternal and civic organization, or group holding an alcoholic beverages license, regardless of the percent of change of corporate officers; or
A subsequent holder of a license of a deceased licensee if the subsequent holder is the spouse or sibling of the deceased licensee.
